OL,3,CParents create rival primary school
OL,4,Cover RAAC concerns
OL,6,FParents at a school built with a
OL,7,Fdangerous concrete substitute are so
OL,8,Fafraid for kids' safety they've set up
OL,9,Fa rival primary next door.
OL,11,FAround 20 pupils at Gatehouse Primary
OL,12,Fare being kept away by parents, who
OL,13,Ffear it could suffer a catastrophic
OL,14,Fcollapse after the discovery of
OL,15,Freinforced autoclaved aerated concrete
OL,16,F(RAAC).
OL,18,FThe parents claim local authority
OL,19,FCouncil are not taking concerns
OL,20,Fseriously.
