OL,4,Cover RAAC concerns
OL,6,FRebecca said: "I want the report to
OL,7,Fsay the school is 100 per cent safe
OL,8,Fand what it says is to the contrary.
OL,9,FCouncil officials are telling us it is
OL,10,Fsafe. We asked them who told them it
OL,11,Fis safe but they couldn't give us an
OL,12,Fanswer."
OL,14,FLib-Dem leader Alex-Cole Hamilton, who
OL,15,Fhas raised concerns about RAAC, said:
OL,16,F"Despite repeated warnings the
OL,17,FScottish Government has yet to make
OL,18,Ffunds available to make these
OL,19,Fbuildings safe.
