OL,6,F"I don't blame these parents
OL,7,Fwhatsoever. I probably would think
OL,8,Fabout it for my kids if they were in a
OL,9,Fschool at risk of collapse."
OL,11,F"The SNP Government needs to get its
OL,12,Fhead out the sand and urgently make
OL,13,Ffunds available for local authorities
OL,14,Fto fix this."
OL,16,FA Scottish Government spokesperson
OL,17,Fsaid: " have sought to provide
OL,18,Freassurance about the mitigations
OL,19,Falready in place to protect pupils and
OL,20,Fstaff, as well as their longer-term
OL,21,Fplans to replace the school's roof."
